<head>EMPATHY</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">神入</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>ABILITY to IMAGINE INTENSELY BEING a DIFFERENT PERSON one INTERACTS with.</p>
    </div>
